&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;nilpnc&quot; data-start=&quot;834&quot; data-end=&quot;877&quot;&gt;Data Engineering &amp;amp; Pipeline Development&lt;/h3&gt;
