&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;2bfkqk&quot; data-start=&quot;878&quot; data-end=&quot;990&quot;&gt;Design, develop, and maintain scalable ETL/ELT pipelines to support enterprise data integration and analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;l3mfv9&quot; data-start=&quot;991&quot; data-end=&quot;1172&quot;&gt;Ingest, transform, and integrate data from diverse sources, including flat files, JSON, XML, Excel, REST APIs, graph databases, and other structured and unstructured data formats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;xloxk4&quot; data-start=&quot;1173&quot; data-end=&quot;1298&quot;&gt;Develop and optimize SQL and Python-based data processing solutions to support efficient data ingestion and transformation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;11ajega&quot; data-start=&quot;1299&quot; data-end=&quot;1424&quot;&gt;Build and maintain reusable, scalable data workflows that support business intelligence, reporting, and advanced analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
