&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;msiuwv&quot; data-start=&quot;997&quot; data-end=&quot;1095&quot;&gt;Plan and coordinate imagery collection activities to align with operational and mission needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;3lq918&quot; data-start=&quot;1096&quot; data-end=&quot;1184&quot;&gt;Interpret imagery data to identify patterns, anomalies, and actionable intelligence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ub06mo&quot; data-start=&quot;1185&quot; data-end=&quot;1280&quot;&gt;Support geospatial data validation and quality assurance/quality control (QA/QC) processes.&lt;/li&gt;
